description: A pun about a diamond and a duck
title: Diamond Duck
n_1: A jeweler and a duck are talking in a workshop.
c1_1: We tried making a diamond shaped like you.
n_2: The jeweler looks at the duck with a concerned expression.
c1_2: But it quacked under the pressure.
n_4: Both share a moment of understanding.
c1_4: Glad we could laugh about it.
